prompts.frontCover:
A watercolor painting of a humorous and lighthearted birthday scene, flat 2D for greeting card printing. In the center, a cartoon illustrated version of the couple from the reference photo c6a757b1-887d-4951-a22f-727b71cfb9ab. The man, a young East Asian man with short black hair in a tan hoodie, is mischievously attempting to put a tiny, festive party hat on the head of the woman he's hugging from behind. The woman, a young East Asian woman with long black hair and round glasses in a light blue 'ROCKY MO... RIDGE' sweatshirt, has a playfully surprised expression as if she just noticed. They are both smiling warmly. The scene is surrounded by whimsical, floating watercolor splotches in festive colors that look like abstract confetti. In the safe center area, the text "Happy Birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. The style is a soft watercolor painting with flowing colors, visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds. --ar 5:7

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
